name: iXtentia
tag_list: mobile-application-development, iphone-application-development, ipad-application-development, android-application-development, blackberry-application-development, windows-phone-application-development
overview: iXtentia is a division of Extentia Information Technology that focuses on custom application development. Formed in 2009, iXtentia creates softwares for the Apple, Android, Windows Phone, and BlackBerry platforms. It has developed iPhone and iPad applications for brands such as Volvo, LEGO ® , and Hennessy.
